d7ad756cb9fc"],

Cell["\<\
In this section we will try to derive the relations connecting the \
derivatives of Christoffel to the Riemann Curvature tensor and its \
derivatives. (Note that these are all evaluated on the worldline).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9265646383257065`*^9, 
  3.9265647088075447`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2f235ac7-a894-b449-bfc0-\
